  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Almazy: A Gem of Arcade-Puzzle Adventure 💎🪨</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rediscover the charm of a beloved genre with <strong>Almazy</strong>, our homage to the legendary <i>Boulder Dash®</i> series. Embrace the spirit of classics like <i>Repton</i> and <i>Emerald Mine</i>, while embarking on a unique journey that blends nostalgia with fresh excitement.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >A Diamond Hunter's Odyssey ⛏️✨</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Step into the shoes of a daring diamond collector, navigating through caves brimming with challenges. Your journey takes you across intricate mazes filled with precarious boulders and cunning adversaries. <strong>Almazy</strong> combines the thrill of fast-paced arcade gameplay with clever puzzle-solving, offering a balanced experience that’s engaging but never overwhelming.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Strategize, Dodge, and Collect 🎮🧩</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each level is a carefully crafted puzzle demanding both strategy and quick reflexes. With <strong>100 hand-designed stages</strong>, the game promises a fulfilling adventure for long-time fans and newcomers alike. Whether you’re a veteran of 2D arcade puzzlers or discovering the genre for the first time, Almazy has something to captivate your imagination.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features 🌟</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>100 Hand-Crafted Levels</strong> 🏞️ – A diverse range of challenges, each meticulously designed to test your skills.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Arcade + Puzzle Blend</strong> ⚡ – A perfect mix of fast-paced action and brain-teasing strategy.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Dynamic Obstacles & Enemies</strong> 👾 – Stay sharp as the cave throws unexpected challenges your way.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Nostalgic Yet Fresh</strong> 🎶 – A respectful nod to the classics, enhanced with modern touches.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Controller & Joystick Support</strong> 🎮 – Play the way you like.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Embark on this timeless adventure with <strong>Almazy</strong> – where every move counts, every diamond shines brighter, and every level brings a new thrill! 💎🔥</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Almazy: A Gem of Arcade-Puzzle Adventure 💎🪨</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rediscover the charm of a beloved genre with <strong>Almazy</strong>, our homage to the legendary <i>Boulder Dash®</i> series. Embrace the spirit of classics like <i>Repton</i> and <i>Emerald Mine</i>, while embarking on a unique journey that blends nostalgia with fresh excitement.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >A Diamond Hunter's Odyssey ⛏️✨</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Step into the shoes of a daring diamond collector, navigating through caves brimming with challenges. Your journey takes you across intricate mazes filled with precarious boulders and cunning adversaries. <strong>Almazy</strong> combines the thrill of fast-paced arcade gameplay with clever puzzle-solving, offering a balanced experience that’s engaging but never overwhelming.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Strategize, Dodge, and Collect 🎮🧩</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each level is a carefully crafted puzzle demanding both strategy and quick reflexes. With <strong>100 hand-designed stages</strong>, the game promises a fulfilling adventure for long-time fans and newcomers alike. Whether you’re a veteran of 2D arcade puzzlers or discovering the genre for the first time, Almazy has something to captivate your imagination.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features 🌟</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>100 Hand-Crafted Levels</strong> 🏞️ – A diverse range of challenges, each meticulously designed to test your skills.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Arcade + Puzzle Blend</strong> ⚡ – A perfect mix of fast-paced action and brain-teasing strategy.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Dynamic Obstacles & Enemies</strong> 👾 – Stay sharp as the cave throws unexpected challenges your way.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Nostalgic Yet Fresh</strong> 🎶 – A respectful nod to the classics, enhanced with modern touches.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Controller & Joystick Support</strong> 🎮 – Play the way you like.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Embark on this timeless adventure with <strong>Almazy</strong> – where every move counts, every diamond shines brighter, and every level brings a new thrill! 💎🔥</p>",
